WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:17.560
Tina Daniels is 13 years old. She's a star. She can sing and dance. Everyone knows her.

00:17.560 --> 00:25.680
Everyone loves her. They call her curls because she has beautiful curly hair. They all want

00:25.680 --> 00:38.480
her photos. She can have anything she wants. But is she happy? Does she want to be a star?

00:38.480 --> 00:48.760
Tina, why are you eating chocolates? Her mother asks. I like them. They're nice. Tina says.

00:48.760 --> 00:55.240
You're getting fat. And a fat girl doesn't get lots of money in Hollywood. Mrs. Daniels

00:55.240 --> 01:06.840
says. You want the money? I don't. Tina says. Tina's angry with her mother. And Mrs. Daniels

01:06.840 --> 01:15.520
is angry with Tina. Tina leaves the room and cries. Tina is very sad. She doesn't want

01:15.520 --> 01:26.880
to be a star. She wants a quiet life. One day she has an idea. Her school friend, Mary,

01:26.880 --> 01:34.640
has a grandmother called Mrs. White. Old Mrs. White lives in the country, in stone church.

01:34.640 --> 01:43.800
Tina has a photo of Mary in front of Mrs. White's house. It looks very pretty, not like the city.

01:43.800 --> 01:55.880
Tina decides to go there. Tina's at the city station. She's wearing jeans and an old jumper.

01:55.880 --> 02:04.480
People don't know who she is. Where do you want to go, young girl? The man at the ticket

02:04.480 --> 02:14.240
off his arse, sir. Stone church, please. When's the next train? Tina asks. The train

02:14.240 --> 02:25.040
leaves at two o'clock from platform three, the man says. Tina buys her ticket. Tina arrives

02:25.040 --> 02:33.360
at stone church. She sees an old house near the river. It's the house in the photo. There

02:33.360 --> 02:43.200
are flowers and trees in the garden. Mrs. White must live here, Tina thinks. She goes to the front

02:43.200 --> 02:52.640
door and rings the bell. An old lady with white hair and a kind face opens the door. A black cat

02:52.640 --> 03:06.480
comes out too. Good afternoon. Who are you? The old lady are. Oh hello, Mrs. White. My name's Tina.

03:07.600 --> 03:15.600
I'm a school friend of your granddaughter, Mary. Mary's school friend. How nice to meet you.

03:16.240 --> 03:24.160
What are you doing in stone church, Tina? Mrs. White asks. Tina says she hates the city life.

03:25.680 --> 03:35.280
Well, says Mrs. White. Come in and have a cup of tea, my dear. Tina and Mrs. White drink tea and talk.

03:36.560 --> 03:42.160
Mrs. White doesn't know Tina's a star. She doesn't have a television or a radio.

03:43.040 --> 03:54.320
Tina's very happy. Mrs. White says, Tina, you can stay with me for a week, but first you must telephone

03:54.320 --> 04:05.120
your mother. Tina's angry with her mother and doesn't telephone her. Mother says yes. She says to Mrs. White

04:05.760 --> 04:13.360
later. Her face is a little red. Two days later, Mrs. White is taking Tina for a walk.

04:14.800 --> 04:17.600
Look at the lambs, Mrs. White says.

04:20.880 --> 04:27.440
Yes, I love them. I want to be a lamb. They can jump and run and be happy.

04:28.240 --> 04:38.480
Well, you can run and jump and be happy too, Tina. No, I can't. I... Tina, you're young. Run!

04:38.480 --> 04:46.640
Tina's living a very different life in the country. She sees new things all the time.

04:49.520 --> 04:56.560
Now it's night and Tina and Mrs. White are waiting. It's very quiet.

04:58.400 --> 05:04.560
Every night, some hedgehogs come to the garden. Mrs. White puts out food for them.

05:06.640 --> 05:13.440
I love their long brown noses. Mrs. White says, so do I,

05:14.400 --> 05:26.160
Mrs. Tina. Oh, look, Mrs. Tina. A big brown fox is running across the garden. At first, Tina's very

05:26.240 --> 05:30.960
happy to see the fox. There aren't any foxes in gardens in the city.

05:32.560 --> 05:39.520
Then she sees the fox has something in its mouth. The something is Mrs. White's chicken.

05:40.880 --> 05:44.560
Mrs. White is very angry and wants to kill the fox.

05:48.800 --> 05:55.040
Mrs. White and Tina, look at the fox's work. The chickens are making a terrible noise.

05:56.800 --> 06:01.040
We can't have eggs for breakfast in the morning, Tina.

06:02.080 --> 06:06.720
Says Mrs. White. Why not? asks Tina.

06:08.560 --> 06:14.160
Well, the chickens aren't very happy. When they aren't happy, they can't give us eggs.

06:15.200 --> 06:16.400
Mrs. White explains.

06:18.560 --> 06:22.160
For breakfast, Tina has toast and fresh orange juice.

06:22.640 --> 06:27.040
Three days later, Tina is with Bella, a horse.

06:27.600 --> 06:30.960
She loves Bella and gives us some sugar.

06:32.320 --> 06:35.520
Today, the postman has a letter from Mrs. White.

06:36.880 --> 06:44.480
When he sees Tina, he says, I don't believe it. It's curls.

06:45.920 --> 06:49.360
Then he says to her, everyone's looking for you.

06:49.440 --> 06:53.600
Everyone's looking for you. You're in all the newspapers.

06:55.520 --> 06:58.480
He runs to his red band to find his newspaper.

07:01.200 --> 07:03.920
Mrs. White reads the postman's newspaper.

07:05.760 --> 07:11.920
Tina, says Mrs. White. You're the last TV star, aren't you?

07:13.440 --> 07:16.720
I don't understand. Your mother?

07:17.600 --> 07:25.040
Yes, I'm cold, but please don't send me home. I'm happy here with you.

07:27.360 --> 07:34.800
I'm coming with you to see your mother. I've got a good idea, Mrs. White says.

07:37.200 --> 07:40.320
Tina's mother is very happy to see Tina again.

07:41.760 --> 07:43.920
Mrs. White explains her idea.

07:46.800 --> 07:52.240
Tina can go to her friends' school on the island of Guernsey, between England and France.

07:53.840 --> 07:56.880
Tina can have friends there who don't know she's curls.

07:58.320 --> 08:03.600
What? I want Tina to be a star, Mrs. Daniel says.

08:05.600 --> 08:13.200
She wants to be happy. Mrs. White says quietly, Tina's at school in Guernsey.

08:14.000 --> 08:16.960
She has new friends and new interests.

08:18.480 --> 08:21.840
One day, Tina's friend is reading a magazine.

08:23.280 --> 08:25.680
It's about film and television stars.

08:27.280 --> 08:30.560
There are lots of beautiful photos of beautiful people.

08:31.840 --> 08:33.600
Everyone looks very happy.

08:35.600 --> 08:37.040
What a wonderful life.

08:38.160 --> 08:42.320
The friend says, Tina smiles to herself.

08:43.200 --> 08:49.840
Who wants to be a star? She says, I don't...

